title: It's Geos Dance Party NTSC DVD (2002)
description:
Kids can learn all the hottest dance moves from Geo and his crew in this fun instructional release. Known for his work with Pink, J-Lo, Will Smith, and others, Geo brings the best moves to the small screen, breaking everything down from three different angles, so the steps are easy to understand and perform.


Region 1 - NTSC
Chapters - Yes
Extras - None
Language - English
